                            <h2>5 top tips to plan your wedding</h2>
                            <p>Hopefully, those 5 tips on getting started with your wedding arrangements are a helpful starting point. Once again, the whole team here at Wild Roots would love to congratulate you on this fabulous new adventure and don't forget to take the time to soak up all that wonderful engagement bliss in the midst of all those upcoming preparations!</p>
                            
